{"tid":1795830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民進黨大波參選人 好想奶呀奶","createTime":"2019-12-24T08:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T09:19:29.000Z","uid":344031,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"52338ffe83809f90c513ff13f90b4e1df2139ef6","tid":1795830,"uid":344031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2920785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2920785&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=d8f1b58f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2920785&h=969c573d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2920785</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕將代表民進黨參選新北市第12選區的「太陽花女戰神」賴品妤，昨（18）日致詞時超有誠意深深一鞠躬，結果糗撞麥克風。影片傳開後，賴品妤立刻在社群網站上爆紅。過去她大玩Cosplay及穿著泳裝比基尼的辣照也通通被翻出。<br />\n<br />\n身為立委林昶佐助理的賴品妤，在太陽花學運、反媒體壟斷活動都有表現，尤其學運期間與警方對峙的舉動，讓她獲得「太陽花女戰神」的稱號。<br />\n<br />\n昨日她在致詞最後90度大鞠躬，結果忘記與講台保持距離，結果一頭卡在兩支麥克風之間，但她還是用力低頭，硬是擠開左右兩支麥克風，讓麥克風桿插入她的長髮中；可愛又尷尬的影片傳開後，不少網友大呼「戀愛了」！而賴品妤事後也自嘲「謝謝大家排山倒海的梗圖，鄉親的意見我收到了」，更表示「嘔心瀝血擠出的參選聲明，被自己毀於一旦...齁氣氣氣氣氣」。<br />\n<br />\n對此，也有網友挖出賴品妤過去Cosplay、以及穿著泳裝、比基尼的照片，可見賴身材姣好、皮膚白皙，不少網友看了大呼「戀愛了！」、「鼻血止不住」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pwWw26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pwWw26.jpg&h=123b007b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cu2On9M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCu2On9M.jpg&h=8d3b79a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想加入佢助選團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f4936c291a5bc8fcb4fb5d72f987264e4664a3","tid":1795830,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:04:50.000Z","msg":"p圖...."},{"pid":"ce320fc60b6e5ea59320f155fdb428f6a6001f5b","tid":1795830,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d95e752925b99c150007c9953751daa7cef253","tid":1795830,"uid":294121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:08:48.000Z","msg":"左下似40歲<br />\n右上成個aoa yuna咁"},{"pid":"1dd44c25f582d40cd12070b32e59f5380ef254ea","tid":1795830,"uid":166062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"第三張po錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}